  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package targets Model Risk Level 3 following revised consequence analysis. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet required levels. The 'Use error' factor is documented as not-assessed on the basis that analyst-error pathways are deemed irrelevant to an automated CFD workflow — however, the correct encoding for that judgement would be 'not-applicable', and the factor remains materially relevant at MRL 3.",
