      "rationale": "The assessment team determined that use error does not apply to this COU because the CFD workflow is executed through a fully scripted, automated pipeline with no manual post-processing steps, eliminating analyst-introduced error pathways. Accordingly, this factor was not assessed. Note: the appropriate encoding for this determination would be 'not-applicable'; the use of 'not-assessed' here reflects a documentation oversight rather than a deliberate scoping decision, and the factor's influence on hemolysis prediction fidelity at MRL 3 has not been formally evaluated."
